If you want to start project
	$rails start "<<Project Name>>" 	#without ""

If you run project
	$cd "<<Project Name>>"			#without ""
	$rails server

If you want to create controller
	$rails generate controller {ControllerName} {action}	#	{ControllerName}, {action} is controller name and action name

If you create view you must create in
		app/views/{ControllerName}/{viewName}
		- and routing path in file /config/routes.rb (add "get '{controllerName}/{action}'" in class Rails)
		- don't forget declare action in /app/controllers/controller/{ControllerName}
